# College Website Verifier AI

An AI-assisted Python tool that discovers, verifies, and enriches official college websites using search, web crawling, and rule-based verification.

## Features

- 🔍 Searches official college websites using DuckDuckGo
- 🌐 Crawls websites using Playwright
- ✅ Rule-based website verification
- 📧 Extracts official email addresses
- ☎️ Extracts phone numbers
- 📍 Extracts addresses
- 🔗 Collects official social media links
- 📄 Detects important pages (Contact, About, Admission, Faculty, etc.)
- 📊 Saves results directly to Excel
- 💾 Automatic checkpointing and resume support

## Project Structure

