├── README.md
└── .gitignore
```

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/karthikpolasi1818-cmyk/CollegeWebsiteVerifierAI.git
cd CollegeWebsiteVerifierAI

python -m venv .venv

# Windows
.venv\Scripts\activate

pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Run

```bash
python main.py
```

## Technologies

- Python
- Playwright
- BeautifulSoup
- Pandas
- RapidFuzz
- DuckDuckGo Search

## Output

The scraper generates:

- Official Website
- Verification Confidence
- Contact Information
- Social Links
- Important Pages
- Excel Report

